    "title": "Marketplace Manager - Dishis Designer Jewellery - Freshers Welcome",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Marketplace Manager with drive and ambition, Dishis Designer Jewellery in Mumbai is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Dishis Designer Jewellery:\nDishis Designer Jewellery is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mumbai, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Dishis Designer Jewellery!",
